This folder holds PGP keys specifically for signing use in "armored" format.
They may be used for code signing, certificate signing, or key signing.

The recommended filename format is ...

keyid `-` identity `-public.asc`

The keyid should be the long form, 16 hex digits prepended with `0x`.
All keys in this project are public, but `-public` makes that clear
and off-sets the identity from the `.asc` suffix.


